<br>
The one weapon that people talk about most often for an MA is a Claw (Quality Level 1 <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://auno.org/ao/db.php?cmd=view&id=160279)">auno.org/ao/db.php?cmd=view&id=160279)</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> (Quality Level 200 <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://auno.org/ao/db.php?cmd=view&id=160287)">auno.org/ao/db.php?cmd=view&id=160287)</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
You can work out your imps and IP expenditure to use a pretty good claw, but you'll have to use a self equipped one in order to take it off, use an MA attack, then re-equip it.<br>
<br>
I've never used a claw so I can't tell you how well they work. I'd recommend just going fists because you won't have as much of an IP crunch. <p>Bellerephon, Master of All Cool Engi's<br>
